How to Load data into Power BI desktop 7

Click the  data link above    to load the file.



1-      Get Data

2-      Select the Source of your data.

3-      Select the file you want to load.

4-      When the Navigator dialogue box open select the table you want to load.

5-      Preview the table.

6-      Click Load, you will see the table in the Fields.


To learn more about how to load data:
